data.text: All guidelines and policies on changes to an itinerary can be found here: https://t.co/03iQEY7gIm
- If the value of your new ticket is higher than the amount paid for the original ticket, you may cover the difference with the regular payment methods (debit or credit cards).

How the voucher works?
- The voucher will have the total purchase amount (ticket + extras)
- You may use it to fly until June 30th, 2021, either to fly yourself or the person of your preference.
